  "prompt": "What are some good and romantic Malayalam songs?",
  "response": "Malayalam cinema has a rich history of creating beautiful and romantic songs that capture the essence of love and longing. Here are some timeless and soulful romantic Malayalam songs that are loved by audiences:\n\n### Classic Romantic Songs:\n1. **\"Manasa Maine\"** from *Yodha* (1992)\n2. **\"Thumbi Vaa\"** from *Nokkethadhoorathu Kannum Nattu* (1984)\n3. **\"Oru Swapnam Pole\"** from *Nokkethadhoorathu Kannum Nattu* (1984)\n4. **\"Omanathinkal Kidavo\"** from *Omanathinkal Kidavo* (1986)\n5. **\"Kaattinu Thattathe\"** from *Rajavinte Makan* (1986)\n6. **\"Manjalayum Kaattu\"** from *Lekhayude Maranam Oru Flashback* (1983)\n\n### Modern Romantic Songs:\n1. **\"Chundari Penne\"** from *Premam* (2015)\n2. **\"Hemanthamen\"** from *Aniyathipraavu* (1997)\n3. **\"Kannadi Kinnaathey\"** from *Kaazhcha* (2004)\n4. **\"Karukara\"** from *Pathemari* (2015)\n5. **\"Mizhiyilae\"** from *Hridayam* (2022)\n6. **\"Kannullo Neeli Samudram\"** from *Chocolate* (2007)\n7. **\"Oru Koodaiyum\"** from *Bangalore Days* (2014)\n8. **\"Manasse Manasse\"** from *Charlie* (2015)\n9. **\"Hemanthamen\"** from *Aniyathipraavu* (1997)\n10. **\"Ponveyil\"** from *Kireedam* (2007)\n\n### Melodious and Soulful Songs:\n1. **\"Kannalane\"** from *Bombay* (1995) \u2013 Though a Tamil film, it\u2019s widely loved in Kerala.\n2. **\"Ethra Naal\"** from *Njandukalude Naattil Oridavela* (2017)\n3. **\"Nee Mukilo\"** from *Om Shanti Oshaana* (2014)\n4. **\"Aaro Neel Akashe\"** from *Kali* (2016)\n5. **\"Poomuthole\"** from *Jacobinte Swargarajyam* (2016)\n\nThese songs are perfect for creating a romantic ambiance, whether it\u2019s for a special occasion or just to reminisce about love. If you have a specific mood or era in mind, let me know, and I can tailor the recommendations further!",
